風</span></span>屬新活動 送5星龍，火短刀4星<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/140153_55a8c8ca9b36e6a771f114d898b6e300.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F140153_55a8c8ca9b36e6a771f114d898b6e300.png&h=962fddaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140733_f989b1cb06829f08f08f34d075e26037.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140733_f989b1cb06829f08f08f34d075e26037.png&h=f54c71dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=RKA40l2zGTg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRKA40l2zGTg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=sm4UzQuaDl%2B6eTsmviJ43OargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=1179907f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/watch?v=RKA40l2zGTg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>FAQ：</strong></span></span><br />\n點刷首抽？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">完左教學，設定支援(選單＞戰友＞支援角色設定)就夠你兩抽</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n同人合作打有幾多石？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">50石一個人，最多2500石</span><br />\n <br />\n點升戰力？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">升lvl／升環／龍／武器／建築／護符</span><br />\n <br />\n唔夠錢點算？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">打錢副本 / 活動</span><br />\n <br />\n點有多啲瑪那？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">課金以外任何關卡都會提供 / 活動</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">任何素材／金錢／經驗關卡都有機率出現稀有怪，打完有機會提升得到既瑪那</span><br />\n <br />\n四葉草係咩黎同點先有？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">四葉草係餵龍既欣物，打任何素材／金錢／經驗關卡都有機率出現稀有怪，打完有機會掉落</span><br />\n <br />\n建築工匠開幾多個？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">建議4個推快遊戲進度 </span><br />\n <br />\n點造高星武？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">升建築lvl再升主城同鍛造</span><br />\n <br />\n點解武器除哂佢話我裝緊？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">戰友支援角色裝緊</span><br />\n <br />\n武器升邊個？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">升同屬嗰邊, 招技on9都係同屬, 因為同屬1.5x攻</span><br />\n <br />\n咩係520，又咩係434?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">5星2階0突武器，4星3階4突武器(即係滿突4星屬武)</span><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽唔到歌點算好？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">耳筒play / apple watch play / airpod play</span><br />\n <br />\n點解開場等咁耐？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">排隊比人入場</span><br />\n <br />\n新手完咗首抽應該做咩好?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">先打主線，如撞正活動舉行期間則活動優先，拎限時既活動獎勵</span><br />\n <br />\n今日餵乜比隻龍?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hObmQX2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhObmQX2.png&h=0ac71af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n咩係24%龍化?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">16人團體戰中，主控角色裝備活動加攻護符(通常係3星官方送)，其他3名AI裝備8%龍化護符，配合3名隊友開場時就可以即刻龍化(變龍)，加快通關速度</span><br />\n <br />\n8%龍化護符又係邊張?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2星版本: [url] <a href=\"https://dragalialost.gamepedia.com/Dragon_Arcanum[url][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdragalialost.gamepedia.com%2FDragon_Arcanum%5Burl%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=sm4UzQuaDl%2B6eTsmviJ43OargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=5df203f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://dragalialost.gamepedia.com/Dragon_Arcanum[url][/url]</a><br />\n3星版本: <a href=\"https://dragalialost.gamepedia.com/Dragon%27s_Nest \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdragalialost.gamepedia.com%2FDragon%2527s_Nest%20&d=sm4UzQuaDl%2B6eTsmviJ43OargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=0b113979\" target=\"_blank\">https://dragalialost.gamepedia.com/Dragon%27s_Nest </a><br />\n4星版本: <a href=\"https://dragalialost.gamepedia.com/King%27s_Countenance \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdragalialost.gamepedia.com%2FKing%2527s_Countenance%20&d=sm4UzQuaDl%2B6eTsmviJ43OargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=8c952a7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://dragalialost.gamepedia.com/King%27s_Countenance </a></span><br />\n <br />\n平時做哂日任既體力/毛拎嚟做咩好?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">打錢/帝國章</span><br />\n <br />\n邊度睇到我啲角/龍/符/武器既stat?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> Dragalia Lost wiki: <a href=\"https://dragalialost.gamepedia.com/Dragalia_Lost_Wiki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdragalialost.gamepedia.com%2FDragalia_Lost_Wiki&d=sm4UzQuaDl%2B6eTsmviJ43OargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=be9c011a\" target=\"_blank\">https://dragalialost.gamepedia.com/Dragalia_Lost_Wiki</a> </span><br />\n <br />\n課金買咩包好?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">新手必中5星包&gt;$318上限解放組合包&gt;普通金鑽，500金鑽每日充值組合包都係好推薦買 </span><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>其他須知事項：</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">爆發攻擊(蓄力)可以破盾，也可以大幅減少OD(技能槽)，快速進入break狀態</span><br />\n <br />\n紅色預警圈可以使用技能無敵幀擋住，紫色的不行<br />\n昏迷&mdash;&mdash;受到攻擊後方可解除<br />\n黑暗&mdash;&mdash;命中率下降<br />\n濕身&mdash;&mdash;必被暴擊<br />\n冰凍&mdash;&mdash;被同伴攻擊後可解除<br />\n <br />\n真風龍過關推薦要求(待眾幻神補充)<br />\n火屬角(HP最少1700，ATK最少2200)<br />\n屬建30/30，職建16/16<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong> Useful link：</strong></span></span><br />\nWiki: <a href=\"https://dragalialost.gamepedia.com/Dragalia_Lost_Wiki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdragalialost.gamepedia.com%2FDragalia_Lost_Wiki&d=sm4UzQuaDl%2B6eTsmviJ43OargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=be9c011a\" target=\"_blank\">https://dragalialost.gamepedia.com/Dragalia_Lost_Wiki</a><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">詳細數值可以參考以下連結：<br />\n<a href=\